tors? Offer a brief explanation.\r\nExcellent - enjoyed time with the instructors\r\n   5. Did you feel that the monthly training fees mapped well with the services offered?  How do the fees compare to other martial arts schools you know of?\r\nNot a problem\r\n   6. How long did you train at AEMMA before leaving the Academy?\r\nWe appeared for individual (or one off) lessons to see if we were interested in continuing\r\n   7. What caused your long-term absence (no details, just high level description)?\r\nInstructors were great - but above that, the people we dealt with were a little too heavy/serious/stuffy for our comfortability.\r\n   8. What changes or enhancements to AEMMA would be enough for you to consider returning to practices?\r\nNot sure there are any.  We may return regarding of any enchanments or changes.\r\n   9. Would you have any general comments or opinions about AEMMA?\r\nExcellent facility - great concepts - just wasn\\\'t right at the time - and since then have become busy with work to the point that I am not as active as I would like to be.\r\n*******************************'),(173,3,1,1,'AEMMA','Jesse',NULL,'Lewarne','Mr.','Mr. Jesse Lewame','596 Davenport Rd.',NULL,NULL,'Toronto','ON','M5R 1K9','Canada','416.924.1876','416.924.1876',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Dr. Fred Freedman','416.928.0920','http://www.aemma.org/images/bio_photos/bio_noPhotoDbase.jpg','http://www.aemma.org/arms/a/aemma_80.jpg','student','M',0,0,NULL,'1989-08-22',0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'10','Rosedale Heights S.',0,0,NULL,0,'2005-09-11',0,NULL,'2006-01-01',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2005-09-11','Ossington',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(175,3,1,1,'AEMMA','Eldred','T.K.','Weng','','','72 Curzon Street','','','Toronto','ON','','Canada','416.320.4390','416.320.4390','','416.320.4390','eldred.tjie@gmail.com','Shervin Shahidi','647.886.0384','http://www.aemma.org/images/bio_photos/bio_noPhotoDbase.jpg','http://www.aemma.org/arms/a/aemma_80.jpg','computer an